org.zamia.util

Class HashMapArray<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zamia.util.HashMapArray<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K -
    V -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class HashMapArray<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Combination of a HashMap and an HashSetArray, provides: - O(1) access to elements using a key - O(1) access to elements using their index - preserves order of added unique elements (ordered set semantics)
    Author:
    Guenter Bartsch
